    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/48335881/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u48335881-8.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/48335881/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">卡卡</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-04-03"
      class="main-meta">2012-04-03 21:34:34</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5373122_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  近来在工作上、人际关系上很是被动，陷入低潮。不知道是不是占星小组里面说的水星逆行的影响。我似乎把自己陷入了一种四面楚歌的环境中，以高压政策对待下属、员工。某一天，看到李叔同的“威不足而怒，识不足则虑”，有一种醍醐灌顶的感觉。但如何不怒而威，却一直找不到门路...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5373122/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">12有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
